---
import App from "../components/common/App.astro";
---

<App
  title="Privacy Policy - CAPCo Fire Protection"
  description="Learn about how we collect, use, and protect your personal information and cookie usage."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mb-8">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>

      <div
        class="bg-primary-50 dark:bg-primary-900/20 border border-primary-200 dark:border-primary-800 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8"
      >
        <p class="text-primary-800 dark:text-primary-200 mb-0">
          <strong>Last Updated:</strong>
          {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mt-8 mb-4">
        Information We Collect
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-4">
        We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you create an account,
        submit a project, or contact us for support. This may include:
      </p>
      <ul
        class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-6 space-y-2"
      >
        <li>Name, email address, and contact information</li>
        <li>Company information and project details</li>
        <li>Authentication credentials and preferences</li>
        <li>Communications and support requests</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mt-8 mb-4">
        How We Use Your Information
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-4">
        We use the information we collect to:
      </p>
      <ul
        class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-6 space-y-2"
      >
        <li>Provide and maintain our fire protection services</li>
        <li>Process project submissions and manage client accounts</li>
        <li>Communicate with you about your projects and our services</li>
        <li>Improve our website and user experience</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations and protect our rights</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mt-8 mb-4">
        Cookie Usage
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-4">
        We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience on our website. Our
        cookie usage includes:
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-background-card dark:bg-background-card-dark rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mb-3">
            Essential Cookies
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-3">
            Required for basic website functionality, user authentication, and security.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-text-muted dark:text-text-muted">
            These cookies cannot be disabled as they are necessary for the website to function
            properly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-background-card dark:bg-background-card-dark rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mb-3">
            Analytics Cookies
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-3">
            Help us understand how visitors interact with our website by collecting anonymous
            information.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-text-muted dark:text-text-muted">
            You can opt out of these cookies through our <a
              href="/cookies"
              class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">cookie preferences</a
            >.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-background-card dark:bg-background-card-dark rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mb-3">
            Functional Cookies
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-3">
            Enable enhanced functionality and personalization, such as remembering your preferences.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-text-muted dark:text-text-muted">
            These improve your experience but are not essential for basic functionality.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-background-card dark:bg-background-card-dark rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mb-3">
            Marketing Cookies
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-3">
            Used to track visitors across websites to display relevant advertisements.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-text-muted dark:text-text-muted">
            You can opt out of these cookies through our <a
              href="/cookies"
              class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">cookie preferences</a
            >.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mt-8 mb-4">
        Managing Your Cookie Preferences
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-4">
        You can manage your cookie preferences at any time by:
      </p>
      <ul
        class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-6 space-y-2"
      >
        <li>
          Visiting our <a
            href="/cookies"
            class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">Cookie Preferences</a
          > page
        </li>
        <li>Clicking the "Manage Preferences" button in our cookie banner</li>
        <li>Using your browser's cookie settings</li>
        <li>Contacting us directly for assistance</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mt-8 mb-4">
        Data Security
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-4">
        We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information against
        unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. This includes:
      </p>
      <ul
        class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-6 space-y-2"
      >
        <li>Encryption of data in transit and at rest</li>
        <li>Regular security assessments and updates</li>
        <li>Access controls and authentication systems</li>
        <li>Secure data storage and backup procedures</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mt-8 mb-4">
        Your Rights
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-4">
        Depending on your location, you may have certain rights regarding your personal information,
        including:
      </p>
      <ul
        class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-6 space-y-2"
      >
        <li>The right to access your personal information</li>
        <li>The right to correct inaccurate information</li>
        <li>The right to delete your personal information</li>
        <li>The right to restrict or object to processing</li>
        <li>The right to data portability</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mt-8 mb-4">
        Contact Us
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-4">
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact
        us:
      </p>
      <div class="bg-background-card dark:bg-background-card-dark rounded-lg p-6">
        <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-2">
          <strong>CAPCo Fire Protection Systems</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-2">
          Email: privacy@capcofire.com
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark">
          Website: <a
            href="https://capcofire.com"
            class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">capcofire.com</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-border-light dark:border-border-dark">
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-text-muted">
          This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. We will notify you of any material
          changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated"
          date.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</App>
